{"type": "article", "id": 51017, "title": "奥利奥推出可以吃的“游戏机”，Google 地图的马里奥导航挺萌 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人相关的一切", "date": "2018-03-12T04:13:40Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 48341, "name": "恋与制作人"}, {"id": 1941, "name": "肯德基"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 13, "praise_count": 74, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180312120721vykFTVgJSZNmraHK.gif", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">又是跨界</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://beta.techcrunch.com/2018/03/09/mario-can-now-guide-your-route-in-google-maps/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>3 月 10 日是马里奥日，为了庆祝这一天 Google 地图和任天堂合作，用户可以把导航箭头换成开着小车的马里奥。</b></a><br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180312120937FncoMwZ0kPUxyIKG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.128125\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180312120841GlHTrOD5JpSh4FPn.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MzYxMjI0NQ==&amp;mid=2659127366&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=dc25d86db9300d9bdd6d0cc19ea87144&amp;chksm=bd1fd8fc8a6851eac3e2a2c1467bde2051dfa88ec9f6d8d341a84612bf8b506c71ae69871f6d&amp;scene=0&amp;key=ba1ab88e28f6c0ede20c657ddedc68e0ccd8226369137fff48a1fa7ef189d48e5b52cfab0eda67dc3ee2a30589766334fd9ac9a30c3d37d147948c20c7a0ac51dd40e200479596b68f48504f39b508a1&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MTIyNTYzODY0MA%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir6%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.10.5+build(14F2511)&amp;version=11000006&amp;lang=zh_CN&amp;pass_ticket=U0PyMBrj3JrSoB6%2BybLCsigQs8w7n0AfCIb7N%2BNYJeJ26Drdds13bSdhFXxMxIqr\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\" rel=\"nofollow\">肯德基 X 《恋与制作人》白色情人节营销，</a>在 3 月 12 日至 3 月 25 日推出恋与明星餐，同时赠送恋与制作人游戏闪卡一张和专属语音，共 4 款限量发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180312111432sF1SJNk6IgH7pG9V.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.805732\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"http://inln.nen.com.cn/system/2018/03/09/020405840.shtml\" rel=\"nofollow\">可口可乐 X 百度推出 AR 城市罐</a></b>，分别是北京、上海、大连、成都等 16 座中国的城市，需要使用百度 App 扫描城市罐。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180312112037xRXn8h6rzlIOPQD7.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.575000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803121120007D1C2dHpuL5KlymQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">值得一提的案例</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/26189.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>奥利奥推出 AR 营销 Oreo Box</b></a>，扫一扫奥利奥饼干就可以在手机上玩各种小游戏。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180312102707keEBNRQg1snL8byw.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.575000\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803121030457iCcn04WpQMbeAIx.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.575000\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/26175.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>东方航空的微电影广告《一张飞往心底的机票》</b></a>，分别拍摄了两对母子，一对情侣的三个故事线，利用时光倒流的视角展示生活中被忽视的亲情和爱情。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=o0549cyoj1i&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/articles/44039.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>杭州“天竺三寺”之一的法喜寺也开始卖官方周边</b></a>，包括环保袋、明信片、护身符等等。寺庙做周边本来是件挺新鲜的事儿，但如果产品自身的文化属性不强，纯粹只是为了拓展商业收入，未免变得有点俗气。<br></p><p class=\"\">——其实都是看设计。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180312112449DNHxOTRwMdz6A2PE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.883333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803121125385wZzpR2Yn3qgycBW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.810185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://v.qq.com/x/page/i0602dfud2v.html?start=2\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>BBDO 纽约延续了士力架的营销老话题 “You're Not You When You're Hungry”</b></a>。这回的两支广告，是为了给即将上市的新品：花生酱&amp;杏仁士力架预热。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=c06024cefd5&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=i0602dfud2v&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p class=\"\">以及，补充一个挺不错的国际劳动妇女节营销。<a href=\"http://creative.adquan.com/show/43695\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\" rel=\"nofollow\">FCB Inferno 为英格兰运动委员会 （Sport England）设计了一个 “Queen Rules”（王后做主）活动。</a>该活动推出了全新的扑克牌游戏玩法，其中王后地位高于国王。这项宣传活动旨在激发人们就性别平等展开对话。<br></p><p class=\"\">这项活动由博彩公司 Unibet 提供支持，由来自网站 womenwhodraw.com 的 16 位极具才华的女性插画师绘制。这是一个为女性插画师提供支持的网站，尤其是有色人种、LBTQ+（同性恋、双性恋、跨性别者和对其性别认同感到疑惑的人）以及其他少数群体的女性插画师。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180312114826IweFGOfitZKVrdhM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.683333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">题图来源：<a href=\"https://beta.techcrunch.com/2018/03/09/mario-can-now-guide-your-route-in-google-maps/\" rel=\"nofollow\">techcrunch</a></p>"}